{"body":{"coverUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/43","type":"CITY_MP","status":"UNCURRENT","id":17,"name":"鄭勁節","electorate":"台中市第五選區<br>潭子、大雅、神岡","weight":5,"contact":"聯絡我們","support":"支持我們","politics":"政策","declaration":"年輕有衝勁 民意不脫節","areaId":8,"areaName":"台中市","createdAt":"2022-05-25T11:48:00.222Z","candidateAttachments":[{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/950","id":763,"attachmentType":"url","attachmentUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Y23H5BKaSDo","attachmentName":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y23H5BKaSDo","title":"鄭勁節_競選宣言","content":null,"weight":99,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:31:19.340Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/949","id":762,"attachmentType":"image/png","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/5_工作區域 1.png","attachmentName":"02b478e4-50e4-4aa4-87f7-12d1ff785105_.png","title":" ","content":null,"weight":5,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:27:32.455Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/948","id":761,"attachmentType":"image/png","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/4_工作區域 1.png","attachmentName":"ecd24cbc-4dab-46ed-9387-c41c0aa7627d_.png","title":" ","content":null,"weight":4,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:27:31.756Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/947","id":760,"attachmentType":"image/png","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/3_工作區域 1.png","attachmentName":"f4bf52e8-5ea8-4ad6-acc7-a82f253e6514_.png","title":" ","content":null,"weight":3,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:27:31.253Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/946","id":759,"attachmentType":"image/png","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/2_工作區域 1.png","attachmentName":"865d03ad-107a-4c8b-9df9-d84224f2be09_.png","title":" ","content":null,"weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:27:30.637Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/945","id":758,"attachmentType":"image/png","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/1_工作區域 1.png","attachmentName":"bc56082a-50ca-4100-a8a9-f45d1a194d48_.png","title":" ","content":null,"weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T07:27:29.876Z"}],"candidateContacts":[{"id":68,"title":"地址","content":"103台北市大同區延平北路四段 171 號1樓","createdAt":"2022-06-02T01:22:02.057Z"},{"id":69,"title":"電話","content":"02-2598-0802","createdAt":"2022-06-02T01:22:31.038Z"}],"candidateDeclaration":{"id":15,"title":"我是鄭勁節，去年從台大政治所畢業後，我回到台中，在時代力量台中黨部任職。","content":"<p>參選原先並不在我的人生規劃內，但在學了這麼多年的政治後，當我實際投入到政治工作中，我才意識到，政治是一件神奇的事。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>它神奇的地方在於：只要你認真了，你就一定會陷進去。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>你會在聽到員工被雇主要求要檢查衛生棉才給請生理假時，感到憤怒，你甚至會氣自己，為什麼沒辦法避免這種爛事一再發生。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>你也會在拋棄口號、準備好資料，走上街頭與民眾對話公投時，感到振奮、滿足。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>面對無理的攻擊有時你會沮喪，但當你真的有能力替弱勢發出聲音時，你會感到幸福。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>這是我在台中黨部工作幾個月以來，深刻體會到的。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>當然，青年參政也面臨許多困境。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>根據媒體統計，一位議員，平均要花費 500 萬到 800 萬元，來選一次選舉。這個金額，是我用盡全力也無法奢望的數字。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>除了錢，更大的挑戰是世襲政治。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>在台中 65 位市議員中，有 9 位是政二代，今年至少還有 8 位市議員，準備讓自己的孩子接班。如果他們都順利接棒，未來每 4 個台中市議員，就會有一位是政二代。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>我想對這樣的現象提出挑戰。</p>\n<p><br />潭子、大雅及神岡，乃至整個台中，目前仍有許多棘手的問題：房價高漲卻低薪、空汙狀況依舊嚴峻、托育品質良莠不齊⋯⋯。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>我想將我的專業帶進議會，真正回應人民的需求，我想解決問題，我想實踐公平正義。</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.478Z"},"candidateEducations":[{"id":33,"title":"台灣大學政治所","content":null,"weight":3,"createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.484Z"},{"id":34,"title":"台灣大學政治系","content":null,"weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.598Z"},{"id":35,"title":"台中一中","content":null,"weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.664Z"}],"candidateExperiences":[{"id":83,"title":"時代力量台中黨部專員","content":null,"weight":0,"createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.538Z"}],"candidatePolitics":[{"id":84,"title":"以「潭雅神綠園道」為展場，申辦 2024 台灣設計展","content":"","weight":4,"createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.845Z"},{"id":83,"title":"落實親子正義","content":"◼ 增加公托數量\n◼ 落實資訊公開、杜絕違法幼托業者\n◼ 各區共融公園均衡設置，加強品質管理","weight":3,"createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.711Z"},{"id":82,"title":"有效管制空汙","content":"◼ 明定台中減媒期程\n◼ 設立空氣品質維護區\n◼ 提高空汙費費率\n◼ 加嚴高汙染行業別排放標準\n◼ 焚化爐加速更新\n◼ 老舊柴油車課稅、汰舊換新補助\n◼ 加速自行車道、捷運路網建設","weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.652Z"},{"id":81,"title":"實踐居住正義","content":"◼ 設立囤房稅，輔以出租減稅等配套措施\n◼ 公告地價合理調整，確立公告地價的調整基準\n◼ 加速社會住宅興建，增加弱勢保留戶比例","weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.544Z"}],"candidateSocial":{"id":17,"line":null,"facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/jaych3n9","email":null,"instagram":"https://www.instagram.com/jay.cheng/","youtube":null,"createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.560Z"},"candidateSupports":[{"id":33,"title":"戶名:111年臺中市議員擬參選人鄭勁節政治獻金專戶<br>郵政劃撥：22863040 <br>銀行帳號:銀行代號( 700)7000010-22863040","content":" https://donate.newebpay.com/CHENGCHINCHIEH/2022?fbclid=IwAR3ynYd33OxYmSCJT061A0x_oFUjqY9RwaQf1mW13adaRJqvvvjaulfCWXg","weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.552Z"},{"id":34,"title":"看板和志工應援","content":" ","weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-05-29T11:48:00.658Z"}]}}